---
---

<section class="bg-[#1A1816] px-[10px] py-24">
  <div class="bg-[#22201E] rounded-3xl py-24 px-8 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <!-- Headline -->
    <div class="text-center mb-6" data-animate>
      <p class="font-montserrat text-teal text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-4">Vertical Integration</p>
      <h2 class="font-fraunces text-cream text-[clamp(36px,5vw,72px)] leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.02em]">
        We don't route to pharmacies.<br />
        <em class="italic text-terracotta">We are the pharmacy.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center max-w-[640px] mx-auto mb-20" data-animate data-delay="1">
      <p class="font-inter text-cream/50 text-base leading-[1.6]">
        NovaMed is backed by Lake Hills Pharmacy — our own NABP-accredited, state-licensed compounding facility. That means we control quality, speed, and compliance end-to-end. No third-party dependencies. No finger-pointing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Row -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-20" data-stagger>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-[clamp(40px,5vw,64px)] leading-none mb-2">37</p>
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm">State Licenses</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-[clamp(40px,5vw,64px)] leading-none mb-2">116+</p>
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm">Active Clinics</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-[clamp(40px,5vw,64px)] leading-none mb-2">NABP</p>
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm">Accredited</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-[clamp(40px,5vw,64px)] leading-none mb-2">503A/B</p>
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm">Compliant</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Compliance Features -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6" data-stagger>
      <div class="border-t border-teal/20 pt-6">
        <h4 class="font-inter text-cream font-semibold text-base mb-3">
          Batch Testing & Audit Trails
        </h4>
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm leading-[1.7]">
          Every compound is batch-tested for potency and purity. Every protocol step is logged. Every change is traceable. Automatic audit trails satisfy state board inspections without scrambling.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-teal/20 pt-6">
        <h4 class="font-inter text-cream font-semibold text-base mb-3">
          End-to-End Quality Control
        </h4>
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm leading-[1.7]">
          From formulation to fulfillment, we own every step. No reliance on third-party pharmacies means no variability in quality, no communication breakdowns, and no delays you can't control.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-teal/20 pt-6">
        <h4 class="font-inter text-cream font-semibold text-base mb-3">
          Regulatory-Ready Infrastructure
        </h4>
        <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm leading-[1.7]">
          HIPAA-compliant platform with encrypted data at rest and in transit. Consent management, adverse event reporting, and documentation workflows built in — not bolted on.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
